{"tid":871571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"網紅惡整約砲妹挨轟！薔薔怒幹譙9分鐘 網讚：紓壓","createTime":"2018-10-22T04:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T12:37:16.000Z","uid":82917,"like":92,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"df8c0f02d8237f3ebb8a4b41980705722326f327","tid":871571,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"日前YouTuber「Bump男人幫」發布實測約砲女性影片，結果竟在旅館內惡整對方，嘴上說是為了要「教育她」，教導女子要好好保護自己，了解約砲的危險性，不過影片隨即引發爭議，遭到猛烈砲轟，前《黑澀會美眉》薔薔（林嘉凌）也看不下去，拍了一部長達9分鐘的影片，痛斥「要不要送個照妖鏡給你，看看自己的份量？」嗆辣言詞被網友推爆。<br />\n<br />\n雖然事後「Bump男人幫」澄清，影片是為了強調約砲的危險性，且經當事人同意才發布，絕對不是歧視或仇女，仍止不住排山倒海的謾罵，向來作風嗆辣、言詞犀利的薔薔也在臉書發文痛批「是在教訓誰呀？你以為你是誰？要不要送個照妖鏡給你看看自己的份量，哪來的自信和勇氣！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/125542_a61a359e4d7617f845a694a6a38f38e5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F125542_a61a359e4d7617f845a694a6a38f38e5.png&h=737f0c68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/125545_e80023c14a5a0f24288aa9d53bbeb089.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F125545_e80023c14a5a0f24288aa9d53bbeb089.png&h=444c7a66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n薔薔強調，每個人都有性自主權，只要在雙方同意之下，可以為自己的行為負責，況且也沒傷害到其他人，就沒有人有資格評論，更別說教訓，「不知道是哪個年代，清朝？還是裹小腳的年代？你他X的會不會管太多啦！」因此不懂對方有甚麼資格談論人生大道理，最後放話「你那麼瘦小，我一拳就可以把你打倒！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/125600_79fbc798b9748efd607003161375ec03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F125600_79fbc798b9748efd607003161375ec03.png&h=4fb07ad4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然薔薔在長達9分鐘的影片狂噴髒話，還是讓網友看完紛紛大讚，留言「拜託你把他折斷」、「很少聽一個人罵人這麼爽的」、「說的太好啦！現在都什麼年代了！你情我願，做錯什麼了嗎？」、「聽妳罵髒話真的很好笑&hellip;療癒的髒話」、「聽薔薔罵人好紓壓」、「薔薔每次都能說到我心坎裡」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/125703_331a98bff46b5def85f2b59407558524.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F125703_331a98bff46b5def85f2b59407558524.png&h=36122e20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條女好癲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n叫隻濕鳩暗星糖果跟人地學下野啦！<br />\n<br />\n怒屌影片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HZksY4eQ4xw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHZksY4eQ4xw&d=ZBfd9OUnX6ygvTczi0zHcXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=bd753c9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HZksY4eQ4xw</a>"},{"pid":"ba3f81bc3a4db5a8f781ad295fe8ac2c8843b1dc","tid":871571,"uid":82917,"like":37,"dislike":3,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mzzCQf8fL1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmzzCQf8fL1k&d=ZBfd9OUnX6ygvTczi0zHcXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=9fa276d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mzzCQf8fL1k</a><br />\n操你媽壹周刊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377c0101dfd4fbe3f4a5535d02f44b16547342a2","tid":871571,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:02:35.000Z","msg":"onlun99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1597365cd702c2fadeef63580a15e108057ec072","tid":871571,"uid":82917,"like":92,"dislike":2,"score":90,"quote":{"pid":"377c0101dfd4fbe3f4a5535d02f44b16547342a2","tid":871571,"uid":71166,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:02:35.000Z","msg":"onlun99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:04:36.000Z","msg":"佢屌人好撚好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets